---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'February 25, 2026';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — TechMo Electronics"
  description="Read TechMo's Terms of Service. Understand the rules, rights, and responsibilities when using our services."
  canonical="/terms"
>
  <Navbar />

  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0f172a] to-[#1e3a8a] text-white py-14 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <div class="text-5xl mb-3" aria-hidden="true">📜</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 px-4 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-custom">

      <div class="notice-box">
        Please read these Terms of Service carefully before using TechMo's website or services.
        By using our services, you agree to be bound by these terms.
      </div>

      <section aria-labelledby="t1">
        <h2 id="t1">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using the TechMo Electronics website (<em>techmo.lk</em>) or any TechMo service,
        you agree to these Terms of Service and our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.
        If you do not agree, you may not use our services.</p>
        <p>These terms apply to all users including visitors, customers, repair customers, and loyalty programme members.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t2">
        <h2 id="t2">2. Products & Purchases</h2>
        <h3>2.1 Product Availability</h3>
        <p>All products displayed on our website are subject to availability. Prices and product listings
        are for informational purposes and may change without notice. Product images are representative only.</p>

        <h3>2.2 Pricing & Payment</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>All prices are displayed in Sri Lankan Rupees (LKR) inclusive of applicable taxes.</li>
          <li>Purchases must be completed in-store; our website does not facilitate online payment.</li>
          <li>Price quotes via our inquiry form are valid for 48 hours unless otherwise stated.</li>
          <li>We reserve the right to cancel or refuse any order at our discretion.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2.3 Product Inquiries & Reservations</h3>
        <p>Submitting an inquiry or reservation request via our website does not constitute a binding
        purchase. Products are held for a maximum of 48 hours after confirmation, after which the
        reservation may be released.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t3">
        <h2 id="t3">3. Repair Services</h2>
        <h3>3.1 Acceptance of Devices</h3>
        <p>By submitting a device for repair, you confirm that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You are the lawful owner of the device or authorised to consent to repairs.</li>
          <li>You have backed up your data — TechMo is not responsible for data loss during repairs.</li>
          <li>You have disclosed all known issues and prior repairs/modifications.</li>
          <li>Devices with physical damage, liquid damage, or unauthorised modifications may affect warranty coverage.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>3.2 Repair Estimates</h3>
        <p>Estimates are provided in good faith. Final costs may differ if additional faults are discovered
        during diagnosis. You will be notified and must approve any cost exceeding the initial estimate
        before work proceeds.</p>

        <h3>3.3 Uncollected Devices</h3>
        <p>Repaired devices must be collected within 30 days of completion notice. After 60 days, TechMo
        reserves the right to dispose of uncollected devices to recover storage and repair costs,
        with minimum 14 days written notice.</p>

        <h3>3.4 Repair Warranty</h3>
        <p>All repairs carry a 90-day warranty on parts and labour, covering the specific fault repaired.
        This warranty is void if the device is subsequently damaged, tampered with, or subjected to
        liquid damage. See our full <a href="/warranty">Warranty Policy</a> for details.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t4">
        <h2 id="t4">4. Warranty</h2>
        <p>Product and repair warranties are governed by our dedicated <a href="/warranty">Warranty Policy</a>.
        Warranties do not cover accidental damage, misuse, liquid exposure, or normal wear and tear.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t5">
        <h2 id="t5">5. Loyalty Programme</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Loyalty points are awarded at TechMo's discretion and subject to change.</li>
          <li>Points have no cash value and cannot be transferred, sold, or exchanged.</li>
          <li>Points expire after 24 months of account inactivity.</li>
          <li>Fraudulent point accumulation will result in account termination and forfeiture of all points.</li>
          <li>TechMo reserves the right to modify or terminate the loyalty programme with 30 days' notice.</li>
          <li>Redeemed discounts cannot be combined with other promotions unless explicitly stated.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t6">
        <h2 id="t6">6. Website Use</h2>
        <h3>6.1 Permitted Use</h3>
        <p>You may use our website for lawful personal purposes only. You may not:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Scrape, crawl, or harvest content without permission</li>
          <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any system or data</li>
          <li>Submit false, misleading, or fraudulent inquiries</li>
          <li>Use automated tools to submit forms or contact requests</li>
          <li>Interfere with the operation of our website or services</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>6.2 Intellectual Property</h3>
        <p>All content, logos, trademarks, and materials on this website are owned by or licensed to
        TechMo. You may not reproduce, distribute, or modify any content without written permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t7">
        <h2 id="t7">7. Returns & Refunds</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Defective products:</strong> Eligible for exchange or refund within 14 days with original receipt and packaging.</li>
          <li><strong>Change of mind:</strong> We do not offer refunds for change-of-mind purchases on electronics.</li>
          <li><strong>Repair refunds:</strong> If a repair cannot be completed, the diagnosis fee (if applicable) may be charged. No repair fee is charged for incomplete work.</li>
          <li>Refunds are processed via the original payment method within 7 working days.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t8">
        <h2 id="t8">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, TechMo shall not be liable for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Indirect, incidental, or consequential loss or damage</li>
          <li>Loss of data, profits, or business arising from use of our services</li>
          <li>Service interruptions or website downtime</li>
          <li>Third-party actions or content</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Our total liability shall not exceed the value of the transaction giving rise to the claim.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t9">
        <h2 id="t9">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of Sri Lanka. Any disputes shall be subject to the
        exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Sri Lanka.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t10">
        <h2 id="t10">10. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes
        acceptance. Material changes will be communicated via our website.</p>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="t11">
        <h2 id="t11">11. Contact</h2>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <p><strong>TechMo Enterprise (Pvt) Ltd</strong><br />
          45 Galle Road, Colombo 03, Sri Lanka<br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:legal@techmo.lk">legal@techmo.lk</a><br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:+94112345678">+94 11 234 5678</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-10 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="policy-link">Privacy Policy →</a>
        <a href="/warranty" class="policy-link">Warranty Policy →</a>
        <a href="/cookies" class="policy-link">Cookie Policy →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-custom { @apply text-[#334155] leading-relaxed; }
  .prose-custom h2 { @apply text-xl font-bold text-[#0f172a] mt-10 mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100; }
  .prose-custom h3 { @apply text-base font-semibold text-[#0f172a] mt-5 mb-2; }
  .prose-custom p { @apply mb-4 text-[15px]; }
  .prose-custom ul { @apply list-disc pl-5 space-y-1.5 mb-4 text-[15px]; }
  .prose-custom a { @apply text-[#1e40af] hover:underline font-medium; }
  .notice-box { @apply bg-amber-50 border border-amber-100 rounded-xl p-5 mb-8 text-sm text-[#334155]; }
  .contact-card { @apply bg-[#f8fafc] rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5 mt-3 text-sm; line-height: 1.8; }
  .policy-link { @apply inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-[#1e40af] hover:text-[#1e3a8a] transition-colors; }
</style>
